      <h2>We Do Not Collect Personal Data</h2>

      <p>The Traveling Times does not collect, store, or share any personal information about you. There are no accounts, no sign-up forms that ask for your name or age, and no tracking cookies.</p>

      <h2>Local Storage</h2>

      <p>Some features on this site (like dark mode and your reading list) save preferences in your browser using something called <code>localStorage</code>. This data stays on your device and is never sent to us or anyone else. You can clear it at any time by clearing your browser data.</p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>

      <p>We may use privacy-friendly analytics to see how many people visit the site. These tools do not use cookies, do not collect personally identifiable information, and do not track you across the internet.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

      <p>The site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Fonts are loaded from Bunny Fonts, a privacy-friendly font service. Neither of these services tracks you.</p>

      <h2>Questions</h2>

      <p>If you or a parent or guardian has any questions, feel free to email <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>.</p>

